        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(agents): keep message tool for lean source replies",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- keep the `message` tool available in `localModelLean` when the current source reply contract is `message_tool_only`\n- thread `sourceReplyDeliveryMode` through the local-model lean filter in agent tool construction and embedded-run tool projections\n- update local-model/Ollama docs so lean mode is documented as preserving required message-tool delivery\n\n## Verification\n\n- `OPENCLAW_VITEST_MAX_WORKERS=1 node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/agents/local-model-lean.test.ts src/agents/agent-tools.model-provider-collision.test.ts --reporter=dot`\n- `node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check src/agents/local-model-lean.ts src/agents/agent-tools.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/attempt.ts src/agents/local-model-lean.test.ts src/agents/agent-tools.model-provider-collision.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/format-docs.mjs --check docs/concepts/experimental-features.md docs/gateway/local-models.md docs/providers/ollama.md`\n- `node scripts/check-docs-mdx.mjs docs/concepts/experimental-features.md docs/gateway/local-models.md docs/providers/ollama.md`\n- `git diff --check HEAD~1..HEAD`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local` (`autoreview clean: no accepted/actionable findings reported`)\n- Crabbox AWS `cbx_5597cbe46ca8`, run `run_ee0bf39ba03c`: `pnpm check:changed`, exit 0\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: lean local-model mode no longer strips the required visible-reply delivery tool when a source turn is in `message_tool_only` mode.\n\nReal environment tested: AWS Crabbox Linux runner `cbx_5597cbe46ca8` on the post-rebase branch; local focused Vitest through `scripts/run-vitest.mjs`.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `pnpm check:changed` on Crabbox plus the focused local commands listed above.\n\nEvidence after fix: `local-model-lean` and model-provider policy tests prove `message` is kept only for `message_tool_only`; Crabbox run `run_ee0bf39ba03c` passed with exit 0.\n\nObserved result after fix: lean mode still drops `browser` and `cron`, still drops `message` for automatic delivery, and preserves `message` for message-tool-only source replies.\n\nWhat was not tested: live Ollama/channel roundtrip for this exact patch; this is covered at the policy/filter layer and by the changed gate.\n",
